snippet.title: Vikings Pinball - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
[WARNING: Either out of laziness or clear-as-day low-budget nature of many Nostra Games titles, the game uses AI generated images for the title screen, trophy icons, PlayStation Store banner, icon and menu image. The game itself, however, doesn't use any AI generated content, thankfully.]

Fun pinball style battles. Attack the military camps of the holy Roman Empire and crush the legionaries. Choose the right trajectories to inflict as much damage as possible. Shoot down enemies, blow up barrels and collect coins. Free the map from these lazybones!

Developed by NOSTRA GAMES
Also released on PlayStation 5

#ps4 #playstation4 #theforeseenarcade #vikings #vikingspinball #pinball #nostragames
